query:
UPDATE timeslot_assignments t1
        SET
            session_id = t2.session_id
        FROM (
            SELECT id, session_id
            FROM timeslot_assignments
            WHERE (time_slot_id, room_id) IN (($1, $2), ($3, $4))
        ) t2
        WHERE t1.id != t2.id
        AND (t1.time_slot_id, t1.room_id) IN (($1, $2), ($3, $4))
